{"tid":2438371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最高人民法院：嚴懲顛覆及煽動分裂國家等犯罪","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T14:57:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26a104c3b99a53406bf6e0ecec738f70b7b00635","tid":2438371,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"最高人民法院工作報告指，堅決維護國家政治安全，依法嚴懲顛覆國家政權及煽動分裂國家等犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n最高人民法院院長周強發表工作報告，指去年審結一審刑事案件有111.6萬宗，判處罪犯152萬多人，總體呈現下降趨勢，嚴厲打擊境內外敵對勢力滲透，依法嚴懲顛覆國家政權及煽動分裂國家等犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n去年審結2萬多宗涉及貪污賄賂、瀆職等案件，包括對華融前董事長賴小民判處並執行死刑，彰顯懲治腐敗的堅強決心，又懲治涉疫案件。<br />\n<br />\n去年「快審快結」近5500宗涉疫犯罪，有案件涉及隱瞞出境史及假冒慈善機構募捐等，法院建設方面會以零容忍態度，嚴懲司法腐敗。<br />\n<br />\n最高人民法院院長周強：「堅決清除害群之馬，提高群眾工作能力，讓廣大法官在各種紛繁複雜，甚至尖銳激烈的矛盾面前，敢於擔當、敢於碰硬、不迴避、不推卸、不徇私情、秉公處理。」<br />\n<br />\n工作報告又指，去年共審結2萬多宗涉及港澳台案件，簽署內地與香港相互執行仲裁，裁決補充安排。<br />\n<br />\n最高人民檢察院工作報告則指，堅決維護國家安全及社會穩定，堅決貫徹《港區國安法》，支持新疆等地依法防治暴恐犯罪，確保社會大局穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=426636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426636&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=7bc60110\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426636&h=0261041a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=426636</a>"},{"pid":"316c36c8a8c1cbebe99e3f2574ea3952e5e4a7dd","tid":2438371,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"係咪好快就「無法自行審理」戴耀廷同肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"dfde5c325296498731451ccb3ecc5f8b51cf1cb8","tid":2438371,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc090c9ca42a1bfe530a127bcdc66cdb807fe670","tid":2438371,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:41:13.000Z","msg":"最高法院嘅首席法官竟然向習近平述職<br />\n<br />\n喺司法獨立嘅民主國家簡直係天大笑話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKAonuS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKAonuS.jpg&h=3fe0c267&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44106189e32b31188ee7fd2e875764a2fb12f229","tid":2438371,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"316c36c8a8c1cbebe99e3f2574ea3952e5e4a7dd","tid":2438371,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"係咪好快就「無法自行審理」戴耀廷同肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"有乜理由港人陸審？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b138e077a9b8d49beafd7ace03a627935df78cf3","tid":2438371,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYk0pLn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYk0pLn.jpg&h=57c64af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62f2c310b16e064d489fb042c3d6f06f8cf7732c","tid":2438371,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}